"Yo no quiero morir" means?

749
01:13:08,221 --> 01:13:11,557
It's Spanish.
It means "I don't want to die. "

750
01:13:14,268 --> 01:13:16,812
What do you think these ghosts want
when they talk to you?

751
01:13:24,945 --> 01:13:27,113
I want you to
think about it, Cole.

752
01:13:28,656 --> 01:13:32,118
I want you to think about it
really carefully.

753
01:13:32,243 --> 01:13:34,954
What do you think
they want?

754
01:13:38,665 --> 01:13:43,003
-Just hello.
-That's right. That's what I think too.

755
01:13:43,128 --> 01:13:45,547
They just want hello,
even the scary ones.

756
01:13:45,672 --> 01:13:48,758
I think I might know a way
to make them go away.

757
01:13:48,883 --> 01:13:51,761
How?

758
01:13:51,886 --> 01:13:54,263
Listen to them.

759
01:13:55,681 --> 01:13:58,017
What if they
don't want hello?

760
01:13:58,142 --> 01:14:01,436
What if they're just angry and they
just want to hurt somebody?

761
01:14:01,561 --> 01:14:03,855
I don't think
that's the way it works.

762
01:14:03,980 --> 01:14:06,608
How do you know
for sure?

763
01:14:08,026 --> 01:14:10,778
I don't.

764
01:14:20,037 --> 01:14:22,205
[Door Opens, Closes]

765
01:14:30,046 --> 01:14:33,174
- [Engine Starts]
- Hey !

766
01:14:33,299 --> 01:14:36,218
- [Tires Squealing]
- Hey ! Hey !

767
01:14:52,650 --> 01:14:56,737
[Lynn Sobbing] What's happening?

768
01:14:56,862 --> 01:15:01,116
[Whispering]
What's happening?

769
01:15:02,534 --> 01:15:05,745
Go !
[Sobbing]

770
01:15:05,870 --> 01:15:08,831
[Quietly Sobbing]

771
01:15:12,585 --> 01:15:15,129
[Breathing Heavily]

772
01:15:17,548 --> 01:15:20,259
What's happening
to you?

773
01:15:20,384 --> 01:15:23,595
Is someone hurting you?
I'll kick their ass.

774
01:15:23,720 --> 01:15:26,890
Cole, if they're
hurting you-- [Sobbing]

775
01:15:29,225 --> 01:15:31,602
[Moans]

776
