[Whimpering]

781
01:16:40,832 --> 01:16:44,002
[Sobbing]

782
01:17:38,260 --> 01:17:41,555
[Swallowing]

783
01:17:41,680 --> 01:17:46,518
[Gagging, Panting]

784
01:17:46,643 --> 01:17:48,978
[Sobbing]

785
01:17:49,103 --> 01:17:51,856
I'm feeling
much better now.

786
01:17:56,360 --> 01:17:59,321
[Quivering] Do you want to
tell me something?

787
01:18:18,088 --> 01:18:20,132
[Hydraulic Brakes Hissing]

788
01:18:27,597 --> 01:18:29,724
[Gasqs]

789
01:18:35,187 --> 01:18:38,023
She came a long way
to visit me, didn't she?

790
01:18:39,483 --> 01:18:42,152
I guess she did.

791
01:19:16,100 --> 01:19:19,019
[Sobbing]

792
01:19:28,152 --> 01:19:30,279
Can you get
some water ?

793
01:19:34,158 --> 01:19:36,076
That's her sister.

794
01:19:53,926 --> 01:19:58,263
You know, when I went through this
with my father's cancer--

795
01:19:58,389 --> 01:20:01,641
I just can't imagine a child
being in bed for two years.

796
01:20:01,767 --> 01:20:04,227
[Woman] How many--
How many doctors?

797
01:20:04,352 --> 01:20:07,230
- I think it was six.
- Six different doctors?

798
01:20:07,355 --> 01:20:09,691
I think so, yes.

799
01:20:15,571 --> 01:20:20,033
I just heard the, uh,
little one is falling ill now.

800
01:20:20,158 --> 01:20:22,411
God hello them.

801
01:20:41,928 --> 01:20:44,431
Don't go home,
okay?

802
01:20:44,556 --> 01:20:46,975
I definitely won't.

803
01:21:42,234 --> 01:21:44,861
Aah !
[Panting]

804
01:22:45,417 --> 01:22:47,794
Mister ?

805
01:22:50,838 --> 01:22:53,174
Excuse me, mister.

806
01:22:57,511 --> 01:22:59,972
Are you
Kyra's daddy?

807
01:23:13,442 --> 01:23:16,987
It's for you.

808
01:23:17,112 --> 01:23:20,198
Sh-She wanted
to tell you something.

809
01:23:53,771 --> 01:23:56,106
