810
01:23:58,317 --> 01:24:00,861
[Kyra's Voice] Oh, no, here he comes.
He's coming my way. Psst !

811
01:24:05,573 --> 01:24:08,409
Would you like to dance?

812
01:24:08,534 --> 01:24:12,455
Well, actually,
I just came with my friends.

813
01:24:12,580 --> 01:24:14,999
Oh, well,
how about this?

814
01:24:15,124 --> 01:24:18,502
We can dance for a little bit,
and if you don't like the way I dance,

815
01:24:18,627 --> 01:24:20,545
