[All Laughing]

854
01:29:16,817 --> 01:29:20,112
[Chattering]

855
01:29:21,655 --> 01:29:24,532
[Malcolm] I thought you were
really great in the play, Cole.

856
01:29:24,658 --> 01:29:26,785
- Really?
- Yeah.

857
01:29:26,910 --> 01:29:29,287
- You know what else?
- What?

858
01:29:29,412 --> 01:29:33,833
