sucked big time. [Chuckles]

859
01:29:33,958 --> 01:29:36,543
[Chuckles]

860
01:29:41,048 --> 01:29:44,384
I got an idea how you can talk
to your wife.

861
01:29:44,509 --> 01:29:47,679
Wait till
she's asleep.

862
01:29:47,804 --> 01:29:51,349
Then she'll listen to you
and she won't even know it.

863
01:29:58,605 --> 01:30:01,775
I'm not gonna see you
anymore, am I ?

864
01:30:03,944 --> 01:30:06,780
I think we said everything
we needed to say.

865
01:30:08,281 --> 01:30:11,284
Maybe it's time to say things
to someone closer to you.

866
01:30:13,285 --> 01:30:16,372
Maybe we can qretend like we're
gonna see each other tomorrow.

867
