Okay.

869
01:30:33,888 --> 01:30:36,348
I'm gonna go now.

870
01:30:42,437 --> 01:30:44,814
I'll see you
tomorrow, Cole.

871
01:31:05,166 --> 01:31:07,919
- [Siren Blaring]
- [Chattering, Indistinct]

872
01:31:12,089 --> 01:31:15,593
I'm okay, Officer.
l-I'm okay.

873
01:31:15,718 --> 01:31:17,970
I don't know
what happened.

874
01:31:23,308 --> 01:31:26,227
[Lynn] Hmm.

875
01:31:26,352 --> 01:31:29,439
Geez, I hope
nobody got hurt.

876
01:31:32,650 --> 01:31:35,736
You're very quiet.

877
01:31:35,861 --> 01:31:39,114
You're mad I missed
the play, aren't you?

878
01:31:39,239 --> 01:31:41,575
I have two jobs, baby.

879
01:31:41,700 --> 01:31:44,619
You know how important
they are for us.

880
01:31:44,744 --> 01:31:46,621
[Sighs]

881
01:31:46,746 --> 01:31:49,123
I'd give anything
to have been there.

882
01:32:01,093 --> 01:32:03,345
I'm ready to communicate
with you now.

883
01:32:08,600 --> 01:32:10,643
Communicate?

884
01:32:12,228 --> 01:32:14,563
Tell you my secrets.

885
01:32:16,190 --> 01:32:18,609
What is it?

886
01:32:22,404 --> 01:32:25,156
You know the accident
uq there?

887
01:32:25,281 --> 01:32:28,243
Yeah.

888
01:32:28,368 --> 01:32:30,411
