890
01:32:32,788 --> 01:32:36,292
A lady.

891
01:32:36,417 --> 01:32:38,627
She died.

892
01:32:38,752 --> 01:32:41,171
Oh, my God.
What, you can see her ?

893
01:32:42,672 --> 01:32:45,717
- Yes.
- Where is she?

894
01:32:49,303 --> 01:32:53,182
Standing next to
my window.

895
01:32:59,313 --> 01:33:02,232
Cole, you're
scaring me.

896
01:33:02,357 --> 01:33:04,651
They scare me too
sometimes.

897
01:33:07,320 --> 01:33:09,530
They?

898
01:33:12,450 --> 01:33:14,326
Ghosts.

899
01:33:18,747 --> 01:33:21,208
You see ghosts, Cole?

900
01:33:23,376 --> 01:33:26,171
They want me to
do things for them.

901
01:33:29,048 --> 01:33:31,217
They--
They talk to you?

902
01:33:31,342 --> 01:33:34,428
They tell you
to do things?

903
01:33:35,554 --> 01:33:38,474
They're the ones
that used to hurt me.

904
01:33:39,975 --> 01:33:42,686
What are you
thinking, Mama?

905
01:33:42,811 --> 01:33:47,440
- You think I'm a freak?
- Look at my face.

906
01:33:47,565 --> 01:33:50,485
I would never think that
about you. Ever.

907
01:33:51,819 --> 01:33:54,238
- Got it?
- Got it.

908
01:34:01,578 --> 01:34:03,622
Just let me think
for a minute.

909
01:34:07,542 --> 01:34:09,585
Grandma says hi.

910
01:34:13,089 --> 01:34:16,216
She says she's sorry for
taking the bumblebee pendant.

911
01:34:16,342 --> 01:34:18,969
She just
likes it a lot.

912
01:34:21,430 --> 01:34:25,308
- What?
- Grandma comes to visit me sometimes.

913
01:34:27,769 --> 01:34:30,438
Cole, that's
very wrong.

914
01:34:30,563 --> 01:34:33,107
- Grandma's gone, you know that.
- I know.

915
01:34:33,232 --> 01:34:36,485
- She wanted me to tell you--
- Cole, please stop.

916
01:34:36,610 --> 01:34:39,321
She wanted me to tell you
she saw you dance.

917
01:34:41,031 --> 01:34:44,618
She said
when you were little,

918
01:34:44,743 --> 01:34:46,619
you and her
had a fight...

919
01:34:46,744 --> 01:34:49,455
right before
your dance recital.

920
01:34:51,749 --> 01:34:56,420
- [Sniffles]
- You thought she didn't come
to see you dance.

921
01:35:00,299 --> 01:35:02,592
She did.

922
01:35:08,014 --> 01:35:11,809
She hid in the back
so you wouldn't see.

923
01:35:11,934 --> 01:35:14,687
Sh-She said you were
like an angel.

924
01:35:19,358 --> 01:35:21,443
- [Sobbing]
- She said...

925
01:35:21,568 --> 01:35:24,988
you came to the place
where they buried her,

926
01:35:27,240 --> 01:35:29,659
asked her a question.

927
01:35:32,286 --> 01:35:36,498
She said
the answer is...

928
01:35:36,624 --> 01:35:38,542
every day.

929
01:35:41,211 --> 01:35:43,630
What did you ask?

930
01:35:43,755 --> 01:35:46,966
[Sniffles]

931
01:35:47,091 --> 01:35:50,053
[Voice Breaking]

932
01:35:51,637 --> 01:35:54,807
Do--

933
01:35:54,932 --> 01:35:58,602
Do I make her qroud?

934
01:36:01,104 --> 01:36:03,565
[Sobbing]
Mama.

935
01:36:08,319 --> 01:36:10,655
[Sobbing]

936
01:36:21,832 --> 01:36:26,086
[Laughing, Chattering]

937
01:36:32,967 --> 01:36:35,469
[Man] Hi, everybody.
As most of you know,

938
01:36:35,594 --> 01:36:38,180
I'm not
used to doing this,

939
01:36:38,305 --> 01:36:41,892
and I promised Anna
that I'd try not to embarrass her.

940
01:36:42,017 --> 01:36:46,146
