this wonderful day with us.

943
01:36:51,442 --> 01:36:54,236
It's bittersweet almost,
for me,

944
01:36:54,361 --> 01:36:56,530
'cause I hate
giving her up.

945
01:36:56,655 --> 01:36:58,782
[Malcolm] Anna?

946
01:37:00,033 --> 01:37:02,619
[Applause On Television]

947
01:37:08,666 --> 01:37:10,585
I miss you.

948
01:37:16,507 --> 01:37:19,051
I miss you too.

949
01:37:19,176 --> 01:37:21,928
