950
01:37:22,054 --> 01:37:24,764
What?

951
01:37:26,558 --> 01:37:30,144
- What is it?
- Why did you leave me?

952
01:37:30,269 --> 01:37:33,522
I didn't leave you.

953
01:37:36,734 --> 01:37:39,903
[Object Clatters]

954
01:37:54,208 --> 01:37:57,961
[Cole] I see people.

955
01:37:58,087 --> 01:38:00,505
They don't know
they're dead.

956
01:38:04,718 --> 01:38:09,430
- [Malcolm] How often
do you see them?
- [Cole] All the time.

957
01:38:12,141 --> 01:38:13,976
