970
01:39:26,835 --> 01:39:30,046
- Let me see. Put your hand--
- [Groaning]

971
01:39:30,171 --> 01:39:32,381
Oh, God.

972
01:39:37,803 --> 01:39:39,846
- [Breathing Heavily]
- Okay.

973
01:39:45,435 --> 01:39:47,562
[Grunts]

974
01:39:55,611 --> 01:39:58,655
[Sobbing]

975
01:39:58,780 --> 01:40:02,576
