982
01:41:07,969 --> 01:41:10,638
And I needed
to tell you something.

983
01:41:15,476 --> 01:41:18,562
You were never second.

984
01:41:18,687 --> 01:41:21,231
Ever.

985
01:41:23,483 --> 01:41:26,111
I love you.

986
01:41:31,741 --> 01:41:33,909
You sleep now.

987
01:41:35,869 --> 01:41:38,413
Everything will be
different in the morning.

988
01:41:44,586 --> 01:41:47,463
Good night,
Malcolm.

